replies.body:
Oh wow! Seems like someone was a little jealous of yo skills! AFAIK, getting reported for scripting shouldn't get you punished. We have a system that scans for scripts running in the background that, despite its infamy, seems to work rather well and would have caught any Xerath scripts.

Lemme be the one to say, Good Jorb Summoner!

{{sticker:sg-ezreal}}
